      "content": "small actions dont really change the fact that the math is against us. like, how does planting a tree matter when the oceans are dying? it feels like we're just rearranging deck chairs on the titanic. i'm just so tired of pretending there's a light at the end of the tunnel when it's clearly just more darkness.",
